117
00:04:45.705 --> 00:04:46.985
Oh, oh,

118
00:04:47.305 --> 00:04:49.064
grité yo, deténganlo,

119
00:04:49.064 --> 00:04:50.824
ese es Blackstock.

120
00:04:51.224 --> 00:04:53.945
No me importa mucho quién pueda ser,

121
